Set in an alternate-universe Brazil, Michiko to Hatchin tells the story of Hana Morenos.
Hana is routinely abused by every member of her adopted family, that only takes care of
her because the government pays them to do so... until one day, an escaped convict named
Michiko Malandro crashes through their kitchen window on a motorcycle, claiming to be
Hana's real mother. Confused but willing to do anything to escape, Hana agrees to go with her...
